TMA SIG Panel Discussion: Better Data, Better Decisions
How Organizations are Leveraging Leadership Assessments to Improve Their Talent Investments
Join us for the first meeting of our newly integrated Talent Management & Acquisition SIG! The format for this meeting will be an interactive panel of industry experts on how organizations are leveraging assessments to maximize the effectiveness of their hiring and development efforts. We'll examine aspects such as:
 How organizations select the best method for differing needs and levels (high potentials, emerging leaders, etc.)
 The evolving application of predictive analytics to leadership assessments
 Technological trends and its impact on assessing leadership talent
 Aligning assessment processes with diversity goals
 Finding balance between maintaining the validity of the process and enhancing the candidate experience
Moderator:
Makeda Brown, Executive Coach, PVR Consulting
Panelists Include:
Daniel Healey, Senior Vice President & Head of NA HR, SAP
Dr. David Sowinski, Partner, Vantage Leadership
Brittany Moritz, M.S., Consultant, Korn Ferry
Sean Boyce, Founder, StaffGeek
